data.description: Welcome to 37 Woodmere Court! Built in 2021, this single-owner home offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. With three bedrooms, three full bathrooms, and a spacious bonus room, the home provides an ideal setting for modern living. The split-level design lends a unique architectural element to the house that allows for a seamless division of the living spaces. Upon entering the home, you'll find yourself in a bright and welcoming living area that flows effortlessly into an open-concept kitchen and dining space. The kitchen boasts modern appliances and ample cabinet space, making it the heart of the home where you can easily entertain friends and family. Natural light floods in through large windows, creating an inviting atmosphere throughout. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroom, ensuring privacy and convenience. The additional two bedrooms share a well-appointed hallway bathroom. One of the standout features of this home is the large bonus room, which can be transformed to suit your family's needs. It's perfect for a home office, playroom, or even a cozy media room, providing endless possibilities to make it your own. This home also offers a two-car garage, offers convenient parking and extra storage space for your vehicles and belongings. The fenced-in yard ensures a safe and secure space, as well as a private outdoor area for gatherings and relaxation. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your new home!
